data.description: This Amazing 3 Bed, 2 Bath, 2 Car Ranch Home welcomes you with soaring ceilings & a spacious floor plan. You'll appreciate the Kitchen with ample cabinets & countertops, all appliances stay, breakfast bar, dining area, main level luxury vinyl plank flooring, security system, sprinkler system, and maintenance free vinyl siding.   The lower level features a large family room with bar, mini fridge, microwave, & surround sound creating the perfect space for entertaining family & friends.  Grill out on the deck or patio and enjoy the fully fenced backyard.  This incredible home is conveniently located close to schools, parks, & I80. Don't miss this opportunity!
